<view class="container">
  <!-- 沉浸式自定义导航栏 -->
  <view class="custom-nav" style="padding-top: {{statusBarHeight}}px; height: {{navBarHeight}}px;">
    <view class="back-btn" bindtap="goBack">
      <view class="back-icon"></view>
    </view>
    <view class="nav-title">商品详情</view>
    <!-- 右侧胶囊占位 -->
    <view class="nav-right"></view>
  </view>

  <!-- 顶部商品主图轮播 -->
  <view class="swiper-wrap">
    <swiper class="goods-swiper" bindchange="onSwiperChange" autoplay="{{true}}" interval="3000" circular="{{true}}">
      <block wx:for="{{swiperList}}" wx:key="*this">
        <swiper-item>
          <image src="{{item}}" mode="aspectFill" class="swiper-image"></image>
        </swiper-item>
      </block>
    </swiper>
    
    <!-- 轮播图内部的标题覆盖 -->
    <view class="swiper-cover-text">
      <view class="cover-title">短款收腰设计</view>
      <view class="cover-subtitle">立裁胸型-显瘦提气</view>
    </view>
    
    <!-- 轮播指示器 -->
    <view class="swiper-indicator">
      {{currentSwiper}} / {{swiperList.length}}
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- 商品基础信息区 -->
  <view class="info-section">
    <view class="title-share-wrap">
      <view class="goods-title">{{goodsInfo.title}}</view>
      <view class="share-btn">
        <view class="share-icon"></view>
        <text>分享</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    
    <view class="price-wrap">
      <text class="price-symbol">￥</text>
      <text class="price-num">{{goodsInfo.price}}</text>
      <view class="price-tag">特卖价</view>
      <text class="original-price">原价 ￥{{goodsInfo.originalPrice}}</text>
    </view>
    
    <view class="tags-wrap">
      <block wx:for="{{goodsInfo.tags}}" wx:key="*this">
        <view class="tag">{{item}}</view>
      </block>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- 服务与选择区块 -->
  <view class="service-section">
    <!-- 配送 -->
    <view class="service-item">
      <text class="label">配送</text>
      <view class="content">
        <view class="location-icon"></view>
        <text class="value">西成村二组1号门</text>
      </view>
      <view class="arrow"></view>
    </view>
    <!-- 服务 -->
    <view class="service-item">
      <text class="label">服务</text>
      <view class="content">
        <view class="heart-icon"></view>
        <text class="value">上门取货 · 快递发货</text>
      </view>
      <view class="arrow"></view>
    </view>
    <!-- 选择 -->
    <view class="service-item no-border">
      <text class="label">选择</text>
      <view class="content">
        <view class="clothes-icon"></view>
        <text class="value">尺码</text>
      </view>
      <view class="arrow"></view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- 宝贝详情 -->
  <view class="detail-section">
    <view class="section-title">
      <view class="title-bar"></view>
      <text>宝贝详情</text>
    </view>
    
    <view class="detail-desc">
      杰盾润滑油坚守“质量永远领先一步”的价值观打破“符合标准即为合格”的狭隘观念。
    </view>
    
    <image class="detail-image" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1629198688000-71f23e745b6e?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" mode="widthFix"></image>

    <!-- 尺码表 -->
    <view class="table-container">
      <view class="table-row header">
        <view class="td">尺码</view>
        <view class="td">胸围</view>
        <view class="td">衣长</view>
        <view class="td">肩宽</view>
        <view class="td">袖长</view>
      </view>
      <block wx:for="{{sizeTable}}" wx:key="size">
        <view class="table-row">
          <view class="td">{{item.size}}</view>
          <view class="td">{{item.chest}}</view>
          <view class="td">{{item.length}}</view>
          <view class="td">{{item.shoulder}}</view>
          <view class="td">{{item.sleeve}}</view>
        </view>
      </block>
      <view class="table-note">(尺寸单位:cm，因手工测量可能存在1-3cm误差，版衣数据仅供参考，如遇无法确认可咨询客服)</view>
    </view>

    <!-- 推荐表 -->
    <view class="table-container">
      <view class="table-row header">
        <view class="td flex-2">身高(cm)</view>
        <view class="td flex-2">体重(kg)</view>
        <view class="td flex-2">推荐尺码</view>
      </view>
      <block wx:for="{{recommendTable}}" wx:key="height">
        <view class="table-row">
          <view class="td flex-2">{{item.height}}</view>
          <view class="td flex-2">{{item.weight}}</view>
          <view class="td flex-2">{{item.recSize}}</view>
        </view>
      </block>
    </view>

    <!-- 商品说明 -->
    <view class="desc-title">
      <view class="line"></view>
      <text>商品说明</text>
      <view class="line"></view>
    </view>
    
    <view class="desc-box">
      <text class="desc-text">价格说明：
1、特卖价:指商品销售价，是您决定是否购买商品的依据。特卖价可能会根据商品参与特定的活动优惠(补贴、满减、优惠券等)而发生变化，此时唯品会将在页面同时为您标示出商品参与活动优惠后的特卖价。试用商品的特卖价标识为试用价。
2、超V特卖价:超级VIP会员享受专属优惠(折扣、补贴等)后的商品价格，包含超V试用价。
3、划线价:商品会展示的划横线价格并非原价，该价格为品牌零售参考价，采集自商品的吊牌、标签、包装、品牌官网或厂商提供的建议零售价等。由于地区、时间的差异性以及市场行情波动，品牌零售参考价可能与您购物时展示的不一致，仅供您参考。</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- 底部安全区占位 -->
  <view class="safe-area-placeholder"></view>

  <!-- 底部操作栏 -->
  <view class="bottom-bar">
    <view class="icon-group">
      <view class="icon-item">
        <view class="b-icon icon-service"></view>
        <text>客服</text>
      </view>
      <view class="icon-item">
        <view class="b-icon icon-star"></view>
        <text>收藏</text>
      </view>
      <view class="icon-item">
        <view class="b-icon icon-cart"></view>
        <text>购物车</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    
    <view class="btn-group">
      <view class="action-btn btn-cart">加入购物车</view>
      <view class="action-btn btn-buy">立即购买</view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>